--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Polarplot is a browser-based amateur radio QSO visualizer. It accepts
  ADIF log files and renders contacts on an interactive 2D world map and
  3D globe, with geodesic great-circle paths, country flags, band
  filtering, and optional QRZ API integration for contact enrichment.

  To apply these terms to your own modifications of Polarplot, attach
  the following notice to each modified source file:

